## FR-2: Coach Functional Requirements

### FR2.1 – Coach Login
The system shall authenticate coaches with elevated privileges.

### FR2.2 – View Assigned Users (UI + API)
Coaches shall view a list of users they are responsible for.
The same data shall be accessible via an API endpoint.

### FR2.3 – Retrieve Workout History (API)
The system shall provide an API endpoint returning user workouts in JSON.

### FR2.4 – Analyze User Progress (API-driven data)
Coaches shall view performance trends (volume, PR estimates, consistency).

### FR2.5 – Submit Feedback (UI + API)
Coaches shall submit written feedback attached to a user's workout.
A POST API endpoint shall allow feedback submission.

### FR2.6 – Update Existing Feedback
Coaches shall be able to revise previously submitted feedback.

### FR2.7 – Delete Feedback
Coaches shall be able to remove outdated or incorrect feedback.

### FR2.8 – View Feedback History (UI + API)
Coaches shall view all feedback given to a student.
This data shall be available via a GET API endpoint.

### FR2.9 – JSON Response Structure
All coach API responses shall use standardized JSON formats.
